      • getCryptogram

        public String getCryptogram()
        The 3D secure online payment cryptogram. * For Apple Pay, maps to the paymentData.onlinePaymentCryptogram property in the encrypted payment data. * For Google Pay, maps to the paymentMethodDetails.3dsCryptogram property in the encrypted payment data. Not allowed for Google Pay if the paymentMethod is CARD.
